summary: An ordinance abandoning the condemnation proceeding for certain property and property rights for the opening, widening and extending of certain streets in Section 36, Township 26 North, Range 3 East, W. M., contemplated by Ordinance 84367; abandoning the unexpended balance in the appropriation therefor made from the Street Fund under Ordinance 85974 and repealing said Ordinance 84367 and 85974.
